country as a 16-year-old last year. ; Photo, James Conda, left, was No. 2 in 
Southern California at 14; Jon Elsberry won national doubles title. ; Photo, 
Jimmy Brown, left, and Tim Kreysing, an exchange student and top 10 15-year-old 
from West Germany, team at No. 1 doubles. TERESA TAMURA / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
