preserve. MARY WILLIAMS WALSH / Los Angeles Times; Photo, Bill Lishman pilots 
his ultralight aircraft over Ontario escorted by Canada geese in perfect 
formation. RICK EGLINTON 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
