</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA051890-0136 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 220791 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
May 18, 1990, Friday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 1; Column 5; Metro Desk 
</P>
