<P>
FOR SALE: The $17.6-million Irvine Theatre, due to open in October at UCI, is 
up for sale -- seat by seat. . . . A $1,000 donation will get your name on one 
of the upholstered chairs, says executive director Douglas C. Rankin. "We're 
hoping to raise at least $500,000 this way." . . . For a gift of only $999,000 
more, you can get your name on the entire auditorium -- museum directors still 
don't have a million-dollar donor. Mark I. Pinsky and Jan Herman 
</P>
