<HEADLINE>
<P>
SPOTLIGHT /COMMERCIAL REAL ESTATE: A WEEKLY LOOK AT OFFICE AND INDUSTRIAL REAL 
ESTATE IN THE COUNTY. 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
EL TORO COMMERCIAL AND INDUSTRIAL REAL ESTATE 
</P>
<P>
As of Dec. 31, 1989 
</P>
<P>
OFFICE BUILDINGS 
</P>
