Bob Ringwald's Great Pacific Jazz Band plays at My Brother's Place. JOE VITTI / 
Los Angeles Times; Photo, Pat Wilson plays the washboard with the group Jazzin' 
Babies. JOAN ZOPF-PAHOYO / Los Angeles Times; Photo, Bob Ringwald on the banjo 
